{"tid":1126252,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"關於復仇者聯盟四，唔岩聽既說話你想唔想聽？","createTime":"2019-04-26T09:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T09:27:22.000Z","uid":91929,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8234f88a5b92b77e1fa850e8bf4b5f4d3829130","tid":1126252,"uid":91929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">套片簡直就係美國大兵大戰大隻外星人</span><br />\n<br />\n換句話講，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">就係美國高科技版戰狼</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前面時空穿梭解釋得唔清唔楚，又擺一大堆電影名出嚟，又唔知乜春悖論，屌你老尾我輕輕鬆鬆入嚟睇爆谷片，你一開始就同我解釋得清清楚楚唔好？<br />\n<br />\n仲要hardsell女權、黑人，下下呼個陣㭍味睇到真係打晒冷震，仲衰過大學dem beat<br />\n<br />\nIronman又死得冇說服力，簡直就係為死而死。<br />\n<br />\n套戲淨係比漫威fans，女權運動人士，黑人圍爐意淫打飛機<br />\n<br />\n我抱着極大嘅期望去睇，抱着極大嘅失落離開。"},{"pid":"6d8f3fac20563fbcc3448c88d886273dd31f7090","tid":1126252,"uid":91929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"Admin將我標題改到咁鬼短"},{"pid":"b5cd20fc9041a9c283a46c630a7afda35a4f4e1d","tid":1126252,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d8f3fac20563fbcc3448c88d886273dd31f7090","tid":1126252,"uid":91929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"Admin將我標題改到咁鬼短"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e974088400c42fea037a5ab1cc2a3310d720f3","tid":1126252,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d8f3fac20563fbcc3448c88d886273dd31f7090","tid":1126252,"uid":91929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"Admin將我標題改到咁鬼短"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T09:22:08.000Z","msg":"加返個劇透標籤咪唔洗"},{"pid":"9aa0130edaace489f9206b67f8642107bda928fb","tid":1126252,"uid":91929,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82e974088400c42fea037a5ab1cc2a3310d720f3","tid":1126252,"uid":209773,"